headline.print_headline: Feds: No Endangered Birds Killed in Wood Chipper
headline.main: Feds: No Endangered Birds Killed in Wood Chipper

lead_paragraph: No endangered birds died in a wood chipper earlier this month as a company trimmed trees outside a Northern California post office, federal officials said Tuesday.
